 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ustormhaven.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stormhaven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>FAQ/Index Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/23/01 11:27:41 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://web2.airmail.net/naomi/amalgam/forum/stormhaven.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magic 1HS</span><hr size=1> What level are you, Tan?  The velium scims can be looted off the giants in Velious - they're on anything as low as a scout, up to the high elites.  Or, depending on your CHA, they can be purchased from a vendor in Thurgadin (I don't know about Kael) for around 100pp.<br>
<br>
I also don't know what these sell for anymore, but you might want to look at an obsidian scimitar, or a runed falchon.  (The falchon is still probably closer to 500pp). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tanuvasi>Tanuvasi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/23/01 1:29:45 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> I saw the Obsidian Scimitar being sold for 200pp in action yesterday, maybe I'll hold out for one of those.  My highest character is only 30 so I don't think I'm ready for Velious giants yet :( <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulaeg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Laeg</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/25/01 10:32:55 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://chad_dude.homestead.com/files/sigpic_01mini.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magic 1HS</span><hr size=1> You can actually go into Thrugadin and buy coldain velium weapons which are the velium weapons that proc at lv 1. They cost a little under 100PP...I'd check around auction around Thurgadin first and check the vendors around the bank for a regular velium scimitars (sold for aprox. 50PP) before getting the coldain version. Hope that helps.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span cla